      "content": "i spent fifteen years on the neuro-mapping project. fifteen years of my life. and today the data was proven to be a fundamental error. it wasn't just a mistake, it was a hallucination. everything i published, every award, every lecture... it’s all a sham. i'm just a fraud. there's no point in even trying to fix it. there's nothing left for me to do.",
