      "role": "user",
      "content": "liberation? is that what you'd call it? i just keep thinking about how much energy it takes to keep breathing, to keep waking up to this version of me that doesn't even exist. it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, broken thing around. if the performance is finally over, why does it feel so wrong to just... stop?",
